ED_Title: The situation in the temporarily occupied territories of Ukraine
ED_DecisionText: At its 102nd plenary meeting, on 8 September 2022, the General Assembly decided to include the item entitled “The situation in the temporarily occupied territories of Ukraine” in the draft agenda of its seventy-seventh session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/76/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
